@startuml

title Component Diagram for Project Service (Current-State)

skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A80036

database "PostgreSQL\nproject schema" as postgres <<System>>
database "Redis\ndomain registry" as redis <<System>>
node "Ingest Service\ninternal APIs" as ingest_svc <<System>>
queue "Kafka Broker" as kafka <<System>>

package "Project Service" as project_svc {

  package "Delivery" as delivery {
    [Project HTTP Handlers] as project_http <<component>>
    [Campaign HTTP Handlers] as campaign_http <<component>>
    [Crisis HTTP Handlers] as crisis_http <<component>>
  }

  package "UseCase" as usecase {
    [Project UseCase] as project_uc <<UseCase>>
    [Campaign UseCase] as campaign_uc <<UseCase>>
    [Crisis UseCase] as crisis_uc <<UseCase>>
  }

  package "Infrastructure" as infra {
    [Project Repository] as project_repo <<Repository>>
    [Campaign Repository] as campaign_repo <<Repository>>
    [Crisis Repository] as crisis_repo <<Repository>>
    [Domain Repository] as domain_repo <<Repository>>
    [Ingest Client] as ingest_client <<component>>
    [Lifecycle Event Publisher] as lifecycle_pub <<component>>
  }
}

project_http --> project_uc
campaign_http --> campaign_uc
crisis_http --> crisis_uc

project_uc --> project_repo
project_uc --> domain_repo
project_uc --> campaign_uc
project_uc --> ingest_client
project_uc --> lifecycle_pub

campaign_uc --> campaign_repo
crisis_uc --> crisis_repo
crisis_uc --> project_uc

project_repo -[#green]> postgres : CRUD project.projects
campaign_repo -[#green]> postgres : CRUD campaign
crisis_repo -[#green]> postgres : CRUD crisis config
domain_repo -[#red]> redis : read active domains
ingest_client -[#blue]> ingest_svc : internal HTTP\nactivation-readiness / activate / pause / resume
lifecycle_pub -[#orange]> kafka : publish project.lifecycle.*

note right of project_uc
Current lifecycle path:
- public API in project-srv
- internal HTTP to ingest-srv
- local status update in project DB
- Kafka event as secondary propagation lane
end note

legend right
  |= Color |= Protocol |
  | <#green> | PostgreSQL |
  | <#red> | Redis |
  | <#blue> | Internal HTTP |
  | <#orange> | Kafka |
  | <#black> | Internal Call |
endlegend

@enduml
